headline: Uber Eats Adds Citarella and More Regional Favorites to Growing Grocery Marketplace
summary: Uber Eats (NYSE:UBER) is making it easier than ever for customers to get groceries from the local stores they love. Today, Uber Eats announced new partnerships with Citarella, Rouses Markets, Town and Country, Wild Fork and Rosauers Supermarkets, bringing even more regional favorites onto the platform.
